Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Kamala is suddenly talking about increasing the Child Tax Credit. When I was in Office, with the help of my daughter Ivanka, and Senators Tim Scott and Marco Rubio, I doubled the Child Tax Credit, which brought Tax Relief to 39 Million Middle Class Families. Kamala voted against this Bill in 2017 and, in 2021, Democrats let this Tax Cut expire!
